data.description: "Home Sweet Home" This absolute gorgeous like new home is waiting for you.   It offers so much space and beautiful finishes.   Wood flooring in the downstairs living areas, stairs, and upstairs hallway, 2 beautiful fireplaces, and solid surface countertops in your kitchen.   Your master bedroom suite, with double vanity, seperate shower, sunken ceramic trimmed tub, and huge closet is on the first floor and 3 great size rooms upstairs.  You will be anxious to spend countless hours outside on your circular wooden deck that sits approximately 10, and enjoyed in the privacy fenced yard.   This home could be yours "IF" the price is "RIGHT"!
